        <xsd:element name="ChangeRequisition" type="ChangeRequisitionType" id="oagis-id-3334636d6357458585c7f0324620213a">
                <xsd:annotation>
                        <xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The purpose of the ChangeRequisition is to communicate changes to an existing request for goods or services.  This change must refer to the original document and/or item requested.  The change processing assumes replacement of fields sent, with the exception of:  the key fields for the Order and Line.

If any of the Field Identifiers above require changing, that constitutes a cancellation of the request and/or the addition of another Requisition.
</xsd:documentation>
                </xsd:annotation>
        </xsd:element>
